    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not in running order. The exterior has significant damage, including deep scratches, several large dents, and noticeable rust on the rocker panels and wheel wells. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are largely non-functional. Mechanically, the engine requires a complete overhaul, and there are known issues with the transmission. This is strictly a parts car or a major restoration project for someone with the right tools and expertise. It will need to be towed from its current location.",
