    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, which represents an exceptional balance of performance and long-term value. Meticulously maintained and showing clear pride of ownership, this automobile offers a refined driving experience characterized by mechanical integrity and a well-preserved aesthetic. It stands as a premier choice for the sophisticated driver seeking a high-caliber vehicle that has been curated to meet our rigorous standards of quality.",
      "price": 36850.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
